### Cadastro de Usuário
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novo@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Santos"
}

### Login
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login admin
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@aluguel.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Refresh Token
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

"{token}"

### List Branches
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/branches

### Vehicle Categories
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/vehicles/categories

### Busca de Veículos (precisa token)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/vehicles/search?categoryId=1&from=2023-12-01&to=2023-12-05
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Obter veículo por id
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/vehicles/1

### Criar veículo (admin)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "ABC-1234",
  "model": "Fiat Uno",
  "year": 2020,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "branchId": 1,
  "dailyRate": 150.0,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### Atualizar veículo (admin)
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/vehicles/1
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "ABC-1234",
  "model": "Fiat Uno",
  "year": 2020,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "branchId": 1,
  "dailyRate": 140.0,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### Pricing rules
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/pricing/rules

### Create pricing rule (admin)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/pricing/rules
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holiday surcharge",
  "multiplier": 1.25,
  "startDate": "2023-12-24",
  "endDate": "2023-12-26"
}

### Update pricing rule (admin)
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/v1/pricing/rules/1
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holiday surcharge",
  "multiplier": 1.3,
  "startDate": "2023-12-24",
  "endDate": "2023-12-26"
}

### Pré-autorização de pagamento (usuário)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/payments/preauth
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 10,
  "amount": 110.0
}

### Capturar pagamento
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/payments/capture
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": 1
}

### Reembolso
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/payments/refund
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": 1
}

### Obter pagamento
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Meu perfil
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Minhas reservas
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/users/me/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Listar usuários (admin)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {adminToken}

### Obter reserva por id
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Atualizar reserva
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/v1/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2023-12-02",
  "endDate": "2023-12-06",
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

### Cancelar reserva
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/reservations/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Busca de Veículos (precisa token)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/v1/vehicles/search?categoryId=1&startDate=2023-12-01&endDate=2023-12-05
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Criar Reserva (precisa token)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/v1/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "startDate": "2023-12-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-05"
}
